<br>
Bear in mind that my example is from a Shaman perspective, not a warrior.  After debuffing IV, I found myself taking rampage once the fight started.  As the fight continued it stopped.  I never moved, and obviously IV never moved.  Since I had stopped casting at this point, obviously I was generating no additional hate, but somehow the target of Rampage changed.  If the Rampage list were fixed in stone, this would not be possible.  I'd love to hear other explanations of how this happened, but so far as I can tell the list can change. <p>Aesa D'Artegan<br>
