<br>
This isn't the first time we've seen the target of Rampage change during a fight.  It can happen.  What I can't figure out is exactly HOW it happens, other than to speculate that some amount of hate generation affects the Rampage list in some way.  The reason I believe this is that in the cases where I have seen the Rampage target change, it's always been a buffing type caster who inadvertantly took Rampage early in a fight (presumably due to an ill-timed buff or heal), but who generates essentially zero aggro during the fight itself.  Usually Shamans or Enchanters, occasionally Clerics.<br>
<br>
Anybody have any construtive ideas?<br>
<br>
