<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Just beacause you ate the first rampage does not mean you were at the top of the rampage list.<br>
<br>
It means that, of the people in rampage range, you were at the top of that list.<br>
<br>
If someone had gotten on the mobs hate list before you (healing a debuffer, buffing a MT shooting an arrow, singing bard song while a puller social aggrod IV by grabbing an add, whatever) and they moved into rampage range 30 seconds after the fight started, they would be the rampage target and his rampage list did not change.<br>
<br>
In the likely 300+ rampaging mobs (cleared velious bosses, ssra, VT, etc up to 30-40 times each) that I fought up to PoP, no change in rampage target could ever not be explained by the above.<br>
<br>
If you blur the mob, have rampage tank plink and arrow so that he is the sole only person on the mobs hate list, and keep that rampage up, he will never lose rampage as long as he is in melee range and does 1 point or more of hate. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=solinarinnoruuk>Solinar Innoruuk</A> at: 3/4/03 11:05:47 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=frodlin7th>Frodlin7th</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>/cons RED</span><br>  Posts: 326<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/5/03 12:30:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2589.topic&index=40>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Re:</span><hr size=1> Sollinar is exactly right...<br>
<br>
You weren't on top of the rampage list, you were the highest one on the list who was either in range or not feigned.   Receiving the first rampage is not an accurate indicator of the rampage list.<br>
<br>
Rampage is so predictable and repeatable when set up properly that it's laughable. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2589.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2589.topic&start=41&stop=52>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showPrevMessage?topicID=2589.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showNextMessage?topicID=2589.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2589.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.emailToFriend?topicID=2589.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.threadControl?topicID=2589.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2589.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2589.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspac